def is_number(n):
    try:
        float(n)
    except ValueError:
        return False
    return True
# phra afto edw opote TypeError: Could not convert 53.9653.96 to numeric
def clean_price(value):
    if pd.isna(value):
        return None
    try:
        return float(value)
    #RegEx
    except ValueError:
        if isinstance(value, str):
            match = re.search(r'(\d+\.\d+)', value)
            if match:
                return float(match.group(1))
            else:
                return None
        else:
            return None
